<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior bodeguita del medio crockett + isabella afternoon}
<A>__{in the funky yellow restaurant drinking mojitas. they've had lunch served to them at the bar. frosted glasses have sugar on the bottom and are loaded with crushed cuban herbs. the bartender has been there for 40 years. crockett and isabella look like regulars. they've served chicken and plantains. like any restaurant, the people eating at the bar are the regulars. they sit where hemingway sat in the slow part of the afternoon.}
