<D>__{exactly.}
<A>__{crockett's hand is around her waist and slips down her hip as he pulls her closer and takes off her glasses and she puts down her drink and kisses him at the bar and crockett's eyes dwell on her and she looks back at him and, now, knowing what he's thinking...}
